AcceptedByOrganization(address).details: emitted when a planter with address {planter} is accepted by organization

OrganizationJoined(address).details: emitted when an organization join with address {organization}

OrganizationMemberShareUpdated(address).details: emited when a planter with address {planter} payment portion updated

PlanterJoined(address).details: emitted when a planter join with address {planter}

PlanterUpdated(address).details: emitted when a planters data updated (supplyCap , planterType)

RejectedByOrganization(address).details: emitted when a planter with address {planter} is rejected by organization

acceptPlanterByOrganization(address,bool.details: organization can accept planter to be it's member or reject NOTE emit a {AcceptedByOrganization} or {RejectedByOrganization} event

canAssignTree(address).details: check allowance to assign tree to planter

returns._0: true in case of active planter or orgnization planter and false otherwise

params._planter: address of organization member planter to get data

returns._0: true in case of valid planter
returns._1: address of organization that {_planter} is member of it.

initialize(address).details: initialize AccessRestriction contract and set true for isPlanter

params._accessRestrictionAddress: set to the address of AccessRestriction contract

returns._0: true in case of Planter contract has been initialized

join(uint8,int64,int64,uint16,address,ad.details: based on {_planterType} a planter can join as individual planter or member of an organization NOTE member of organization planter status set to pendding and wait to be accepted by organization. NOTE emit a {PlanterJoined} event

params._organization: address of organization to be member of
params._planterType: type of planter: 1 for individual and 3 for member of organization

joinByAdmin(address,uint8,int64,int64,ui.details: admin add a individual planter or member of an organization planter based on {_planterType} NOTE member of organization planter status set to active and no need for accepting by organization NOTE emit a {PlanterJoined} event

params._organization: address of organization to be member of
params._planterType: type of planter: 1 for individual and 3 for member of organization

joinOrganization(address,int64,int64,uin.details: admin add a planter as organization (planterType 2) so planterType 3 can be member of these planters. NOTE emit a {OrganizationJoined} event

manageAssignedTreePermission(address,add.details: return if a planter can plant a tree and increase planter plantedCount 1 time.

params._assignedPlanterAddress: address of planter that tree assigned to
params._planter: address of planter who want to plant tree

returns._0: if a planter can plant a tree or not

manageTreePermission(address).details: check that planter {_planter} can plant regular tree NOTE if plantedCount reach to supplyCap status of planter set to full (value of full is '2')

returns._0: true in case of planter status is active (value of active is '1')

reducePlantedCount(address).details: when planting of {_planter} rejected, plantedCount of {_planter} must reduce by 1 and if planter status is full, set it to active.

updateOrganizationMemberShare(address,ui.details: oragnization can update the share of its members NOTE emit a {OrganizationMemberShareUpdated} event

updatePlanterType(uint8,address).details: planter with planterType 1 , 3 can update their planterType NOTE planterType 3 (member of organization) can change to planterType 1 (individual planter) with input value {_planterType} of 1 and zeroAddress as {_organization} or choose other organization to be member of with input value {_planterType} of 3 and {_organization}. NOTE planterType 1 can only change to planterType 3 with input value {_planter} of 3 and {_organization} if planter planterType 3 choose another oraganization or planter with planterType 1 change it's planterType to 3,they must be accepted by the organization to be an active planter NOTE emit a {PlanterUpdated} event

updateSupplyCap(address,uint32).details: admin update supplyCap of planter NOTE emit a {PlanterUpdated} event

params._planter: address of planter to update supplyCap
params._supplyCap: supplyCap that set to planter supplyCap
